{"tid":1968098,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"睇唔過眼英文補習佬Spencer Lam","createTime":"2020-04-11T12:00:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T05:22:39.000Z","uid":77716,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"82ded0df13ab90c055dcfd26a7bd2a2e701e1890","tid":1968098,"uid":77716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:00:19.000Z","msg":"幫一個睇唔過眼嘅現職中學英文老師開post<br />\n<br />\n首先，拍片教人phonics，但自己連phonics呢個字都讀成「瘋nics」， 另外有啲vowels都讀錯。仲要話咩年紀都可以學phonics&hellip;事實上英文讀音有太多例外，成年人係都學科學化嘅phonetics。 難怪嘅，人哋香港讀心理學畢業邊度識英文/語言學。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/umagazinehk/videos/2614749145465571/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fumagazinehk%2Fvideos%2F2614749145465571%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W4vgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=822bc600\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/umagazinehk/videos/2614749145465571/</a><br />\n<br />\n第二，阿sir講到明要打入支那市場<br />\n<br />\n「Spencer現時主要教授中學生，並且開始教小學生，而近期興起移民潮，不少成人需要進修英語，為他帶來不少發展空間，下一步計劃推出IELTS英語考試課程，而這些課程也可以攝製視頻，化身為網上課程。<br />\n<br />\n除了香港，Spencer也研究過內地市場，因為每年不少內地學生參加DSE考試，對網上英語課程有一定需求，而他本人普通話不俗，只需配上普通話便能銷售至內地市場。網上英語課程可以申請不同資助，包括政府創新科技署的計劃」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.edigest.hk/article/133707/%e5%89%b5%e6%a5%ad/90%e5%be%8c-%e6%a3%84%e5%81%9a-%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8cmt-%e8%bd%89%e9%96%8b-%e8%a3%9c%e7%bf%92%e7%a4%be-%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%81%ab%e9%80%9f%e7%a9%a9%e8%b3%ba9%e8%90%ac%e6%9c%88%e8%96%aa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edigest.hk%2Farticle%2F133707%2F%25e5%2589%25b5%25e6%25a5%25ad%2F90%25e5%25be%258c-%25e6%25a3%2584%25e5%2581%259a-%25e9%258a%2580%25e8%25a1%258cmt-%25e8%25bd%2589%25e9%2596%258b-%25e8%25a3%259c%25e7%25bf%2592%25e7%25a4%25be-%25e5%258d%258a%25e5%25b9%25b4%25e7%2581%25ab%25e9%2580%259f%25e7%25a9%25a9%25e8%25b3%25ba9%25e8%2590%25ac%25e6%259c%2588%25e8%2596%25aa%2F&d=pQk%2FYDfxyk1It%2BdH9Wj1W4vgSq%2BgcR%2FX%2FBaLnjou7zI%3D&h=e2c6d83d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.edigest.hk/article/133707/%e5%89%b5%e6%a5%ad/90%e5%be%8c-%e6%a3%84%e5%81%9a-%e9%8a%80%e8%a1%8cmt-%e8%bd%89%e9%96%8b-%e8%a3%9c%e7%bf%92%e7%a4%be-%e5%8d%8a%e5%b9%b4%e7%81%ab%e9%80%9f%e7%a9%a9%e8%b3%ba9%e8%90%ac%e6%9c%88%e8%96%aa/</a><br />\n<br />\n心理學grad，英文冇A/5**上年都教英文搵90k， 唔知阿sir依家撈成點？<br />\n<br />\n利申：酸葡萄"},{"pid":"813d3e17b40d60764612e8b863d024c3f9bec005","tid":1968098,"uid":11058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:06:53.000Z","msg":"最搞笑係出grammar post教錯grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4180b0562a136d3798884350b0112ef0eac688d","tid":1968098,"uid":92038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"邊間大學心理學grad？"},{"pid":"2d458a279aa6e35127722806d920d087a35ee99d","tid":1968098,"uid":92038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4180b0562a136d3798884350b0112ef0eac688d","tid":1968098,"uid":92038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:14:29.000Z","msg":"邊間大學心理學grad？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:22:28.000Z","msg":"無嘢睇到了"},{"pid":"0192452f12d6bc5b975532c60b834184a744b414","tid":1968098,"uid":45772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:32:12.000Z","msg":"誤人子弟都有嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b136b0a4d3ebab4cdf74e70cf0eb893dda629ab","tid":1968098,"uid":77716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"813d3e17b40d60764612e8b863d024c3f9bec005","tid":1968098,"uid":11058,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:06:53.000Z","msg":"最搞笑係出grammar post教錯grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:32:42.000Z","msg":"誤人子弟，依家啲中學生補習係咪唔睇老師教育背景"},{"pid":"ce2548f7522955f9ccef01276c243556aeabbbf4","tid":1968098,"uid":77716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T12:43:18.000Z","msg":"教育商業化之下搵到錢係威，但本身冇料又要教哂中小學IELTS就唔好啦<br />\n<br />\n<img sr